reviewText: My mistake to order vhs.  Meant to purchase dvd.  Gave to goodwill

I like the different levels as well as different lengths of times, so you can choose what works for you each day.  I feel like you get a pretty complete work out of all areas of the body.  The instructor is encouraging and keeps it fun!

I bought this tape after seeing a coworker working out with it at work a few days a week. She has had it for over 7 years and constantly raved about it. So far I've only worked out with two tapes. What I love about the moves is that they are low impact and you can feel muscles where you never thought you had them. Debbie is a great instructor and you feel like she really cares about your progress. She also gives great advice. I know I will be using these for sometime. Would certainly recommend.
The product is great! and the cosomer service is awesome! they got it to me in 4 days! im soo happy!
